#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/heuristics.md:0
msgid "# triton.heuristics"
msgstr "# triton.heuristics"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/heuristics.md:2
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.heuristics(values)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/heuristics.md:4
msgid "用于指定如何计算某些元参数值的装饰器。这在自动调优成本过高或不适用的情况下非常有用。"
msgstr "Decorator used to specify how certain meta-parameter values are computed. This is particularly useful in scenarios where automatic tuning is too costly or not applicable."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/heuristics.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.heuristics(values={'BLOCK_SIZE': lambda args: 2 ** int(math.ceil(math.log2(args[1])))})\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def kernel(x_ptr, x_size, **META):\n"
"    BLOCK_SIZE = META['BLOCK_SIZE'] # smallest power-of-two >= x_size  最小的 2 的幂 >= x_size\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/heuristics.md:8
msgid "**参数：** `values (dict[str, Callable[[list[Any]], Any]]**)` - 包含元参数名称和计算元参数值的函数的字典。每个这样的函数都接受一个位置参数列表作为输入。"
msgstr "**Parameters:** `values (dict[str, Callable[[list[Any]], Any]]**)` - A dictionary containing meta-parameter names and functions that compute meta-parameter values. Each such function accepts a list of positional arguments as input."

